# Overview
This release is a minor update for XML and JSON serialisation, following testing with  [ISO20022](https://www.iso20022.org/).  XML Serialisation (with dotnet) reflects its age and is does not support references for elements referenced more than once in an XML document.

This release adds anotations to Hiperspace and HiLang to exclude Stringified key (`SKey`) and `owner` references from XML and JSON serialisation.

---

## Referenced libraries
External references have been updated to the latest version
